headline: Jim Renacci details his plans for Ohio
author: NationalWatch
sentences:
OAN Newsroom
UPDATED 8:00 AM PT – Saturday, January 22, 2022
In May, Ohio Governor Mike Dewine will face-off against former GOP congressman Jim Renacci in the GOP primary.
In an interview with OAN’s Caitlin Sinclair, Renacci detailed his plans for the state of Ohio.
